{"tid":2201522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"守護網絡自由　捐收益助抗爭　 ProtonVPN 創辦人　義無反顧撐港人","createTime":"2020-09-14T00:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T03:10:16.000Z","uid":271829,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"421ccaf4f219fac6581978f5e7243b8b96c30bd6","tid":2201522,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:41:59.000Z","msg":"【Proton創辦人●專訪】守護網絡自由 捐收益助抗爭 義無反顧撐港人<br />\n...<br />\n自由崩落，穹蒼塌下，誰可補青天？<br />\n台灣出生、美國成長的80後科學家嚴育銓（Dr Andy Yen）去年透過創辦的加密電郵支持港人抗爭，今年再捐出旗下加密VPN部份收益，支援香港民間組織，力撐站在網絡自由之戰最前沿的香港。他反監控，護私隱，深信民主自由的價值，同時亦深明對手的強大，自覺公司規模細小，不敢當補天女媧，但認為理念是戰勝的關鍵：「若我們所有人都相信我們可以帶來改變，也嘗試帶來改變，我深信我們將會帶來改變。」<br />\n小公司大理念，眾志成城，人人可以是女媧。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200914/R3D2SOU42BEJZLQU466ZOPYWQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200914%2FR3D2SOU42BEJZLQU466ZOPYWQU%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8CwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=48e2ee23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200914%2FR3D2SOU42BEJZLQU466ZOPYWQU%2F&h=31390c96\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200914/R3D2SOU42BEJZLQU466ZOPYWQU/</a>"},{"pid":"c6068c0aad76874c74ad48ea9e84df6c62122971","tid":2201522,"uid":359563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:45:15.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"b12e342fb2f7e1efd84a4b7f7f3e24543e75ee0f","tid":2201522,"uid":184952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"146f65bf5e60ef93bcb12bb893a6b535f262890a","tid":2201522,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T01:42:40.000Z","msg":"一直用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4ec1efa22bd9237c01205eba74adfb8e9483f3","tid":2201522,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:10:16.000Z","msg":"又係台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif